-- Sony Is Continuing Talks With Sharp on Production of LCD Panels
-- B y   M a r i k o   Y a s u
-- 2010-11-29T00:40:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-29/sony-is-continuing-talks-with-sharp-on-production-of-lcd-panels.html
Sony Corp. is continuing talks with
Sharp Corp. to jointly make liquid-crystal display panels,
Shigenori Yoshida, a Tokyo-based spokesman for the company, said
by phone today.   The two companies are discussing on the collaboration and
Sony may increase its stake in Sharp’s LCD plant in Sakai City,
Western Japan, to as much as 34 percent by the end of April, he
said.     To contact the reporter on this story:
